snippet.textDisplay:
I'm sorry, but SBMM has ruined this game.
It is now MY goal to remain in Bronze FOREVER so I can up my K/D ratio for my main Mirage.
Number of Kills in this game are WAY MORE FUN than camping to Champion.
MY Mirage's .82 KDR has been on a SLOW climb from .48 since Season 1 but YOUR SBMM has made the climb PAINFUL!

Step 1: Wait 2 weeks for all of the Frustrating Pro players to leave Bronze Rank before playing Rank.
Step 2: Play Ranked with Mirage and finally get the 10 kills per match I deserve until I reach Bronze I.
Step 3: Play as Gibraltar (hate him) and keep dying and tanking back down to Bronze IV.
Step 4: Rinse & Repeat

Remember Respawn, I've been writing, emailing, calling, texting, messaging, chatting, posting about fixing the ranking system to a Kills per game based system since Season 2 but you guys won't listen to me. I KNOW what will take APEX to next level and now I'm going to have to take matters into my own hands.
